          <li>We are not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages</li>
          <li>Our total liability is limited to fees paid in the past 12 months</li>
          <li>We are not responsible for third-party service failures</li>
          <li>You use our Services at your own risk</li>
        </ul>

        <h2><i class="fas fa-user-shield text-blue-600 mr-2"></i>10. Indemnification</h2>
        <p>
          You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Spentiva and Exyconn from claims arising from:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your use of our Services</li>
          <li>Your violation of these Terms</li>
          <li>Your violation of third-party rights</li>
          <li>Content you submit through our Services</li>
        </ul>

        <h2><i class="fas fa-gavel text-blue-600 mr-2"></i>11. Dispute Resolution</h2>
        
        <h3>11.1 Governing Law</h3>
        <p>
          These Terms are governed by the laws of [Your Jurisdiction], without regard to conflict of law principles.
        </p>

        <h3>11.2 Arbitration</h3>
        <p>
          Any disputes will be resolved through binding arbitration rather than in court, except you may assert claims in small claims court.
        </p>

        <h2><i class="fas fa-sync-alt text-blue-600 mr-2"></i>12. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may modify these Terms at any time. We will notify you of material changes via:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email to your registered address</li>
          <li>In-app notification</li>
          <li>Website banner</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance. If you disagree, you must stop using our Services.
        </p>

        <h2><i class="fas fa-file-alt text-blue-600 mr-2"></i>13. Miscellaneous</h2>
        
        <h3>13.1 Entire Agreement</h3>
        <p>These Terms constitute the entire agreement between you and Spentiva.</p>

        <h3>13.2 Severability</h3>
        <p>If any provision is found invalid, the remaining provisions remain in effect.</p>

        <h3>13.3 No Waiver</h3>
        <p>Our failure to enforce any right does not waive that right.</p>

        <h3>13.4 Assignment</h3>
        <p>You may not assign these Terms. We may assign them without notice.</p>

        <h2><i class="fas fa-envelope text-blue-600 mr-2"></i>14. Contact Information</h2>
        
        <p>For questions about these Terms, contact us:</p>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <p><strong>Spentiva by Exyconn</strong></p>
          <p><i class="fas fa-envelope mr-2"></i>Email: <a href="mailto:legal@spentiva.com">legal@spentiva.com</a></p>
          <p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt mr-2"></i>Address: 123 Business Street, Tech City, TC 12345</p>
          <p><i class="fas fa-phone mr-2"></i>Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-purple-50 p-8 rounded-2xl mt-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            <i class="fas fa-thumbs-up text-blue-600 mr-2"></i>
            Thank You for Choosing Spentiva
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We appreciate your trust in our platform. These Terms are designed to create a fair and transparent relationship. If you have any questions or concerns, our support team is always here to help.
